00:09:47,667 --> 00:09:50,504
un ikh vel oyfklern di sibe far vos.

216
00:09:52,890 --> 00:09:55,156
ven men hot mir gebrakht in AUSCHWITZ,

217
00:09:55,574 --> 00:09:59,621
dos ershte, d-, mistame dem tsveytn tog zayendik in AUSCHWITZ

