00:11:09,550 --> 00:11:12,340
mayn tate hot gegat a fraynd, a inzhenyer,

238
00:11:12,460 --> 00:11:14,210
velkhe hot gegat a shayn,

239
00:11:14,224 --> 00:11:16,619
dos heyst, aroy- a rekht aroystsuforn

240
00:11:17,534 --> 00:11:20,367
fun Byalistok. iz er geforn in AUGUSTÓW.

241
00:11:20,480 --> 00:11:21,681
AUGUSTÓW.

242
00:11:21,340 --> 00:11:23,247
AUGUSTÓW, dos iz a shtetl

243
00:11:23,480 --> 00:11:25,619
nisht vayt fun Byalistok.

244
00:11:29,015 --> 00:11:30,038
un

