00:11:33,250 --> 00:11:37,154
mayn tatn az er hot a shayn un er ken aroysforn fun Byalistok,

247
00:11:37,666 --> 00:11:40,870
un er fort dortn boyen a vile far a daytsh.

248
00:11:42,340 --> 00:11:46,240
