250
00:11:49,240 --> 00:11:50,310
"tu mir a toyve.

251
00:11:50,660 --> 00:11:52,898
dortn zaynen shoyn nisht faran keyn yidn.

252
00:11:52,900 --> 00:11:54,340
nem mit mayn Fanyen.

253
00:11:54,596 --> 00:11:57,735
zi vet efsher gefinen a plats far undzer zun."

254
00:11:58,240 --> 00:12:00,805
un dos iz geven der tsil fun mayn forn.

