00:12:01,450 --> 00:12:03,642
iz ven ikh bin gekumen in AUGUSTÓW,

256
00:12:03,642 --> 00:12:06,270
hob ikh oysgeton di lates, aropgenumen

257
00:12:06,270 --> 00:12:09,362
di lates fun beyde zaytn, getrogn zeyer a fayne kleydele,

258
00:12:09,362 --> 00:12:12,199
az di goyim zoln nisht aynfaln az do geyt a yid,

259
00:12:12,199 --> 00:12:17,530
der inzhenyer iz nisht gegangen mit mir. er hot getro- un oyf der anderer zayt fun, fun der gas,

260
00:12:17,530 --> 00:12:20,290
