268
00:12:49,013 --> 00:12:49,990
hot a kleyn

269
00:12:49,990 --> 00:12:52,687
sheygetsl, vi ikh hob dir frier gezogt, fun tsen yor,

270
00:12:52,687 --> 00:12:54,362
ongevizn mit dem finger,

271
00:12:54,571 --> 00:12:56,222
az ikh bin a yidishe.

272
00:12:56,943 --> 00:13:01,083
un s'hot nisht gegolfn der lakhn un der redn un, vos heyst,

273
00:13:01,571 --> 00:13:04,966
