290
00:13:42,757 --> 00:13:44,594
s'iz geven a groyse turme,

291
00:13:44,594 --> 00:13:48,617
vos dortn flegt men haltn politishe arestirte zeyer a sakh.

292
00:13:49,757 --> 00:13:53,176
iz in Lomzher turme zaynen shoyn geven a bisl yidn,

293
00:13:53,478 --> 00:13:57,292
vos m'hot gebrakht nokh der likvidatsye fun Byalistok,

294
00:13:58,594 --> 00:14:00,385
hot men zey gebrakht in Lomzhe.

295
00:14:00,408 --> 00:14:02,059
un mir hot men tsu zey...

296
00:14:02,222 --> 00:14:04,962
iz ikh bin geven in, m'hot mir arayngefirt in a ts-

297
00:14:04,962 --> 00:14:07,354
in eyn tsel, vos s'hot badarft zayn eyn mentsh,

298
00:14:07,354 --> 00:14:09,571
un dortn zaynen shoyn geven zibn meydlekh.

299
00:14:11,338 --> 00:14:13,292
un dortn hob ikh ongehoybn

300
00:14:13,617 --> 00:14:16,687
mayn karyere vi a turme-zitserin.

301
00:14:17,989 --> 00:14:20,090
un ikh vel keyn mol nisht fargesn,

302
00:14:20,090 --> 00:14:23,361
zitsndik in turme hot men arayngevorfn a, a froy,

