00:14:56,710 --> 00:14:58,268
a prakht fun a meydl!

316
00:14:58,408 --> 00:15:00,664
un di meydl, ven m'hot undz gefirt

317
00:15:01,919 --> 00:15:04,757
keyn Shtuthof, hot geshprungen fun ban,

318
00:15:04,757 --> 00:15:07,670
fun a kleynem fentsterl, fun, vos heyst,

319
00:15:07,670 --> 00:15:08,896
zeyer kleyn.

320
00:15:08,896 --> 00:15:11,989
hot geshprungen fun ban kedey zikh tsu rateven.

