00:15:22,733 --> 00:15:24,490
a vokh, a vokh tsvey?

326
00:15:24,175 --> 00:15:25,477
ye ye, nisht mer.

327
00:15:25,384 --> 00:15:27,290
un vi lang in Lomzhe bistu geven?

328
00:15:26,849 --> 00:15:28,803
in Lomzhe bin ikh geven lenger.

329
00:15:29,175 --> 00:15:30,896
biz in eyn tog,

330
