334
00:15:35,930 --> 00:15:38,370
di mener bazunder un froyen bazunder,

335
00:15:38,779 --> 00:15:42,060
un s'iz geven nokh dortn a shreklekher epizod.

336
00:15:42,314 --> 00:15:44,430
s'iz geven fun a kleyn shtetl

337
00:15:44,430 --> 00:15:45,454
a yid

