346
00:16:04,630 --> 00:16:08,593
ale kinder zol men haltn links un di ervoksene zoln zayn rekhts.

347
00:16:09,174 --> 00:16:11,500
hobn ale kinder, s'iz geven dortn a sakh mit kinder,

348
00:16:12,820 --> 00:16:16,090
