355
00:16:29,780 --> 00:16:31,663
dir gebn mayn kind?!"

356
00:16:31,756 --> 00:16:33,174
iz tsugegangen der daytsh,

357
00:16:33,174 --> 00:16:34,500
un genumen dos pitsele,

358
00:16:34,570 --> 00:16:36,663
un hot es genumen far di fislekh,

359
00:16:36,663 --> 00:16:38,802
un hot es a klap geton in moyer,

360
00:16:38,802 --> 00:16:41,340
un oyf, p- in al- in onveznheyt fun ale.

361
00:16:41,340 --> 00:16:43,360
der moyer iz tseshpritst gevorn

362
00:16:45,070 --> 00:16:45,520
oyf...

363
00:16:51,918 --> 00:16:53,593
oyfn moyer.

