00:16:54,523 --> 00:16:57,790
un dos iz zakhn vos s'hot zikh mir ayngekritst in zikorn.

365
00:16:58,918 --> 00:17:02,011
un fun dortn hot men glaykh undz gefirt in Shtuthof

366
00:17:02,453 --> 00:17:04,890
fun der turme,

367
00:17:04,890 --> 00:17:07,070
fun Lomzher turme, nokh tsvey khadoshim,

368
00:17:07,760 --> 00:17:09,010
zaynen mir avek

369
00:17:09,521 --> 00:17:09,962
in

