00:17:30,540 --> 00:17:33,880
azoyernokh az zey hobn nokh nisht, zey hobn nisht gehat tsu ton mit keyn yidn,

377
00:17:33,880 --> 00:17:37,732
un dortn, mir zaynen geven di ershte grupe yidishe meydlekh vos m'hot gebrakht in Shtuthof.

