00:17:37,848 --> 00:17:43,197
zaynen mir dortn geven, un a teyl hot gegarbet in amunitsye un a teyl zaynen geblibn in, nisht, mit...

379
00:17:43,197 --> 00:17:44,080
s'iz nisht geven.

