00:18:14,639 --> 00:18:17,499
mayne ershte⟨r⟩ tsvey teg,

390
00:18:17,499 --> 00:18:18,660
ven mir zaynen arayn

391
00:18:20,780 --> 00:18:21,910
in AUSCHWITZ,

392
00:18:23,103 --> 00:18:24,778
dos ershte vos m'hot geton,

393
00:18:24,894 --> 00:18:26,987
m'hot dir gegaltn in kvarantane.

394
00:18:27,243 --> 00:18:29,196
ober far der kvarantane

395
00:18:32,685 --> 00:18:34,522
hot men undz arayngenumen

396
00:18:34,522 --> 00:18:36,406
un opgerazirt di kep,

397
00:18:36,406 --> 00:18:37,410
in gantsn,

398
00:18:37,410 --> 00:18:40,382
opgerazirt vu a mentsh hot a hor, altsding,

399
00:18:40,499 --> 00:18:42,090
un du host geshtanen azoy

400
00:18:42,090 --> 00:18:47,220
