00:19:02,987 --> 00:19:08,243
hobn zikh ongekhapt efsher tsen meydlekh az zey kenen zeyer sheyn zingen un zey viln zingen.

408
00:19:08,801 --> 00:19:10,243
eyn froy,

409
00:19:10,243 --> 00:19:14,452
mistame iz zi dan geven finef un tsvantsik, tsi fir un tsva-, a prakht fun a froy.

410
00:19:14,452 --> 00:19:17,173
hot zikh avekgeshtelt naket un farshtelt,

411
00:19:17,173 --> 00:19:19,917
in gantsn m'hot ir naket, un hot azoy gehaltn di hent,

412
00:19:20,149 --> 00:19:22,963
un zi hot nisht gekent keyn daytsh mistame.

413
00:19:22,963 --> 00:19:24,521
hot genumen zingen,

414
00:19:25,033 --> 00:19:28,173
