00:22:47,145 --> 00:22:48,611
men hot dir geshlogn,

487
00:22:48,890 --> 00:22:50,285
oykh nisht mentshlekh,

488
00:22:50,285 --> 00:22:52,936
un m'hot dir gegebn dortn eyn mol a tog a bisl zup.

489
00:22:53,378 --> 00:22:55,424
dos iz geven di kvarantane.

490
00:22:55,611 --> 00:22:57,634
