491
00:22:57,634 --> 00:22:59,262
in meshekh fun a,

492
00:23:00,076 --> 00:23:01,262
a monat,

493
00:23:01,850 --> 00:23:04,680
hot men undz genumen, oysgeklibn di yunge mentshn,

494
00:23:04,820 --> 00:23:06,052
avekgeshikt

