499
00:23:19,540 --> 00:23:22,401
hot men avekgeshikt arbetn in a shnayderay,

500
00:23:23,110 --> 00:23:25,060
un in der shnayderay

501
00:23:27,913 --> 00:23:31,657
hot men zey gepaynikt, m'hot zey geshlogn, zey hobn gegat,

502
00:23:31,819 --> 00:23:34,540
mir zaynen geven mistame mer nutslekh far zey.

503
00:23:34,889 --> 00:23:36,460
emes tsu zogn,

504
00:23:36,460 --> 00:23:38,913
hobn mir dortn geton azelkhe za- zakhn

505
00:23:38,913 --> 00:23:42,930
vos di daytshn hobn nisht gekent nutsn, nisht di koyln vos mir hobn gegaltn in hant,

506
00:23:42,930 --> 00:23:44,350
nisht di ale zakhn,

507
00:23:44,500 --> 00:23:46,750
ober mir zaynen geven di nutslekhe.

508
00:23:46,750 --> 00:23:48,790
iz mir hot men nisht azoy geshlogn.

509
00:23:49,796 --> 00:23:51,866
un eyn tog geyendik,

510
00:23:51,866 --> 00:23:55,099
der rutin iz geven dortn a zeyer posheter.

511
00:23:55,440 --> 00:23:58,215
men flegt oyfshteyn fir far tog, dir oyfvekn,

512
00:23:58,730 --> 00:24:04,541
un me flegt dir avekshteln sh- zumer in di hitsn, vinter in der grester kelt, di shneyen,

513
00:24:04,820 --> 00:24:06,517
