514
00:24:06,983 --> 00:24:09,355
hot men dir avekgeshtelt oyfn gas.

515
00:24:10,076 --> 00:24:11,610
un oyfn gas

516
00:24:12,564 --> 00:24:14,169
hot men dir gedarft tseyln.

