00:26:02,470 --> 00:26:05,350
avu ikh hob gegarbet, take in dem fabrik vos ikh zog dir,

550
00:26:06,098 --> 00:26:08,098
iz dortn geshtanen a froy,

551
00:26:08,098 --> 00:26:09,121
a kleyne,

552
00:26:10,350 --> 00:26:11,430
antshuldik,

553
00:26:14,010 --> 00:26:15,493
a eltere far mir,

554
00:26:16,307 --> 00:26:17,702
un zi hot

